title: Bakhtiari: Packers' defense is 'unbelievable'
text:
Bakhtiari: Packers' defense is 'unbelievable' Brett Christopherson , Post-Crescent Media 9:15 a.m. EDT October 6, 2015 Green Bay Packers running back Eddie Lacy (right) was Monday's guest on Clubhouse Live with David Bakhtiari. The show is held at The Clubhouse in downtown Appleton. (Photo: Ron Page/Post-Crescent Media) 
Green Bay Packers left tackle David Bakhtiari co-hosted Monday's Clubhouse Live, Gannett Wisconsin Media's live weekly football show. Packers running back Eddie Lacy was Bakhtiari's guest. 
Among the topics they touched on were blocking for Aaron Rodgers, the play of the defense and the Packers' 4-0 start. The show can be seen live at The Clubhouse Sports Pub & Grill in downtown Appleton or at clubhouselive.com . 
Here are select and edited answers from the interview: Clubhouse Live takes place with special guest Eddie Lacy at the Radisson Paper Valley Hotel in Appleton.
